{"tid":2489853,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"李家超：港獨分子仍死心不息　本土恐怖主義潛伏在社會","createTime":"2021-04-15T08:05:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T08:14:09.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2399b8acdb582648eca357b60c7e01a0f02535ef","tid":2489853,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T08:05:34.000Z","msg":"保安局局長李家超表示，必須警惕及防範香港面對著的國家安全風險，「港獨」分子雖然已收斂，但仍然死心不息，繼續以不同方式鼓吹和滲透，利用媒體、文化、藝術、刊物等灌輸「港獨」意識，荼毒年輕人，美化暴力。他說，本土恐怖主義潛伏在社會，要防範自我激化的人，表面平常，但可突然變成「孤狼」，做出恐怖行為。<br />\n<br />\n他在「全民國家安全教育日」主題講座視像發言時說，由2019年「黑暴」至今，有22宗涉及爆炸品、槍械和子彈的案件，檢獲了6支真槍、1000多發子彈以及大量不同類型爆炸品，又指這些爆炸品都是外國恐襲常用的炸藥，警方至今就相關案件拘捕了92人，起訴了38人，最近一宗是兩個月前發生。<br />\n<br />\n李家超說，外部勢力插手香港事務，透過供應資金、物資、進行思想灌輸等，推動和支持暴徒的暴行，外部勢力將資金包裝成不同的「基金」，在香港推波助瀾。<br />\n<br />\n他又提到，個人資料「武器化」亦是國家安全風險，前年及去共有超過5500宗「起底」個案，至今有13人因「起底」及發布犯罪信息被起訴，5人已經被法庭定罪，其中1人被判監禁2年，政府正積極推進修訂《私隱條例》，將「起底」行為刑事化。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1585944-20210415.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1585944-20210415.htm&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sJKhd8YmQljH21R%2F5cbT5WU%3D&h=edf36541\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1585944-20210415.htm&h=7983e4fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1585944-20210415.htm</a>"},{"pid":"2f7885dc978dfd1e5231e9b5349f41042937fe5c","tid":2489853,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T08:09:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"118db659645ed492a81af45985cf54e687d6f552","tid":2489853,"uid":115579,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T08:10:22.000Z","msg":"黄竹坑日日都出緊恐怖分子"},{"pid":"e3cd341206528a5e2296beb2d40f7de3ca454461","tid":2489853,"uid":156652,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T08:10:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcwjC9NsdRMd62LUTXmf1S3q9sSKsYqkWy8qwfRxyRCsM?filename=XbouTS9.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXbouTS9.gif&h=f2809131&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4033140eb04777232640d651ea0f65cd969ef9f1","tid":2489853,"uid":243380,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T08:12:33.000Z","msg":"高壓獨裁反烏托邦社會入左香港就真"},{"pid":"34e565d413faa59529440a5c67334c18439fa59e","tid":2489853,"uid":327462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T08:13:27.000Z","msg":"核平香港咪搞掂囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1114df50dbddc9f1bb7668d978ecb7d41161cf0","tid":2489853,"uid":35125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T08:14:09.000Z","msg":"賤種"}]}